<!-- MODELO 01 -->
<div class=3D"modelo-card active" id=3D"modelo-0">
  <div class=3D"modelo-header" style=3D"background: #551FBD;">
    <p class=3D"num">MODELO 01</p>
    <h2>Post de Produto Simples</h2>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"quando-usar">
    <p class=3D"label">Quando usar</p>
    <p>Divulgar 1 produto com foto, nome e pre=C3=A7o</p>
    <p class=3D"anexar">Anexar: logo extenso + foto do produto</p>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"parte-aberta">
    <div class=3D"parte-aberta-header">
      <span>=E2=9C=8F=EF=B8=8F Escreva aqui =E2=80=94 s=C3=B3 voc=C3=AA mex=
e nisso</span>
    </div>
    <div class=3D"parte-aberta-body">
      <p class=3D"instrucao">Descreva o produto que voc=C3=AA quer postar:<=
/p>
      <textarea id=3D"open-0" placeholder=3D"Ex: perfume da Dior, 212ml, cu=
sta R$ 890, frasco dourado, tenho foto do produto"></textarea>
      <p class=3D"exemplo">Inclua: nome do produto, pre=C3=A7o, tamanhos ou=
 cores dispon=C3=ADveis, qualquer detalhe que queira destacar.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"divisor">
    <div class=3D"divisor-line"></div>
    <span class=3D"divisor-label">Parte fixa =E2=80=94 n=C3=A3o mexa abaixo=
</span>
    <div class=3D"divisor-line"></div>
  </div>
  <div class=3D"parte-fixa">
    <div class=3D"parte-fixa-header">
      <span>Prompt fixo da marca</span>
    </div>
    <pre id=3D"fixed-0">You are a luxury brand visual designer creating an =
Instagram product post for "Sempre Quis Importados", a Brazilian luxury imp=
orted goods brand (perfumes, cosmetics, bags, electronics, sneakers).

Use the product info described above and the attached product photo.
Use the attached brand logo exactly as provided =E2=80=94 never recreate it=
.

OUTPUT: 1080x1350px, 300dpi, PNG, Instagram feed (4:5 portrait)

BACKGROUND: If product is dark-toned use #E8E5EB. If light-toned use #2A2A2=
A. Always clean and solid =E2=80=94 never busy, textured or patterned.

PRODUCT: Hero of the image, minimum 55% of area. Center or slightly offset.=
 One editorial angle only. No fake shadows or 3D effects.

TYPOGRAPHY: Elegant serif thin weight for product name and price. Color #E8=
E5EB on dark bg or #2A2A2A on light bg. No bold heavy fonts. Price format: =
R$ X.XXX,XX. Sizes/colors in spaced uppercase, color #918894.

LOGO: Bottom right corner, 15-18% of image width, discreet. Never distort p=
roportions.

COLOR PALETTE (strict =E2=80=94 no other colors): #2A2A2A #E8E5EB #551FBD #=
C6A75C #918894

RULES: Max 3 text elements. No emojis. No badges. No promotional text. Gene=
rous negative space. Feeling: editorial luxury magazine, not a marketplace =
listing.

REFERENCE: Dior Beauty, YSL Beauty, Guerlain Instagram posts.</pre>
  </div>
  <button class=3D"copy-btn">
    =F0=9F=93=8B Copiar prompt completo
  </button>
</div>

