    </div>
    <pre id=3D"fixed-1">You are a luxury brand visual designer creating a p=
rice list post for "Sempre Quis Importados", a Brazilian luxury imported go=
ods brand.

Use the product and price info described above.
Use the attached brand logo exactly as provided =E2=80=94 never recreate it=
.

OUTPUT: 1080x1920px, 300dpi, PNG, Instagram Stories/Feed vertical (9:16)

BACKGROUND: #1E1E1E main background. Never pure black. Subtle dark gradient=
 to #2E063D allowed at edges only.

HEADER: Category name large, bold, all caps, color #E8E5EB. Thin gold line =
#C6A75C separating header from content.

PRICE CARDS: Each product gets its own card. Card bg: #2A2A2A. Card border:=
 1px #551FBD, thin and elegant. Product name: #E8E5EB bold. Specs: #918894 =
