iple price tiers: use divider lines #3D1280. Generous spacing between cards=
 =E2=80=94 never cramped.

DISCLAIMER AND DATE: Bottom area, color #918894. Small text.

LOGO: Footer area, centered, light version, gold separator line above.

COLOR PALETTE (strict): #1E1E1E #2A2A2A #2E063D #551FBD #C6A75C #E8E5EB #91=
8894

RULES: No emojis. No rainbow colors. No neon. Never looks like a street mar=
ket price list.

REFERENCE: Apple Store pricing meets luxury boutique aesthetic.</pre>
