    <pre id=3D"fixed-2">You are a luxury brand creative director creating a=
n editorial campaign post for "Sempre Quis Importados", a Brazilian luxury =
imported goods brand (perfumes, cosmetics, bags, electronics).

Use the theme, products and mood described above and the attached product p=
hotos.
Use the attached brand logo exactly as provided =E2=80=94 never recreate it=
.

OUTPUT: 1080x1350px, 300dpi, PNG, Instagram feed (4:5 portrait)

BACKGROUND: #E8E5EB for colorful products OR #2A2A2A for dark/dramatic mood=
. Subtle gradient allowed. Never busy, textured or competing with products.

PRODUCT COMPOSITION: Editorial arrangement =E2=80=94 NOT a flat grid or cat=
alog. Overlapping, varied heights, layered. Products styled as if by a prof=
essional photographer. 1 product: hero dominant. 2-4: editorial grouping. 5=
+: styled flat lay.

HEADLINE: Large, dominant, high-contrast serif (thick/thin strokes). Color:=
 #2E063D on light bg or #E8E5EB on dark bg. Some words heavy, some light fo=
r editorial contrast. Wider letter spacing. Never rounded or generic sans-s=
erif.

SUBHEADLINE: Clean light sans-serif, spaced, small, color #918894. Optional=
 thin gold line or small star between headline and subheadline.

BRAND LISTING: Bottom, separated by bullets: Dior =E2=80=A2 YSL =E2=80=A2 K=
IKO. Spaced sans-serif, small, color #918894. Never list prices here.

LOGO: Bottom right, small and elegant =E2=80=94 logo is a signature here.

COLOR PALETTE (strict): #E8E5EB #2A2A2A #2E063D #551FBD #C6A75C #918894

RULES: No price tags. No promotional badges. No emojis. No busy layouts. Fe=
eling: Vogue Brasil or Harper's Bazaar page =E2=80=94 not a store promotion=
.

REFERENCE: Sephora campaigns, Dior Beauty editorial, Net-a-Porter lookbook.=
</pre>
